data.description: Boasting a surprising twist, at first glance, it may resemble other homes in the community, but as you step inside, you'll discover its hidden gem—a massive 1,210 square foot, two-story addition in the back. Complete w/fireplace, charming wood plank ceiling, a spiral staircase leading to an office that could easily serve as a sixth bedroom. Master wing features an ensuite bath. Three dining areas, a generously sized centralized kitchen, and a delightful screened-in atrium, hot tub, fenced yard. Hosting a family gathering, lively event: This home accommodates every occasion with style. Located in a A+ neighborhood, no HOA, walking distance to downtown Coral Springs, The Walk. Known for its vibrant community. Residents enjoy regular get-togethers, happy hours, block parties, dining downtown.
